dialog.body: Hello, thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is George Jones. May I have your name, please?
Hello, my name is Shirley Evans.
Nice to meet you, Shirley. Can you please provide me with your policy number?
Sure, my policy number is eight two four seven six.
Thank you, Shirley. Additionally, could you provide me with your date of birth for verification purposes?
Of course, my date of birth is one two three one, nineteen eighty-five.
Thank you for verifying your information, Shirley. Is there anything specific you need assistance with today regarding your auto insurance policy?
I would like to inquire about adding another vehicle to my policy.
I can assist you with that, Shirley. Let's go ahead and gather the necessary details about the new vehicle you wish to add. Please provide me with the make, model, and year of the vehicle.
Thank you for your time, Shirley. I will proceed with updating your policy. If you have any further questions or need assistance in the future, feel free to contact us again.
